  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下医疗支付改革中的博弈结构。核心是一个成本转移博弈，我称之为Shift节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Shift"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Shift是起点。它向下游连接什么？是单一关系还是多分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Shift"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Shift同时引出两个并行机制：Placement game（医疗机构选址博弈）和Pressure（公共信号压力）。后者是个关键枢纽。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Shift",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Shift到Place和Press的分支已建立。我注意到Place和Press之间也有互动？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Shift",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Place会影响Press，形成反馈。然后Press再向下游分叉：一边是Clinical risk（临床风险），另一边是Signalling game（信号博弈）。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Press",
        "Risk",
        "Signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Press到Risk和Signal的连接已完成。Risk和Signal之间有关系吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Press",
        "Risk",
        "Signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Risk会反向作用于Signal，形成循环。而Signal的终点是Bargaining game（议价博弈），这是整个系统的核心交易环节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Signal到Barg已连接。Bargaining game还有其他输入来源吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Signal",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有，Definition game（定义博弈）也指向Barg。而Define的上游是Coding game（编码博弈）和Compliance game（合规审计博弈）。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Define",
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "Audit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Code和Audit是并行指向Define，然后Define指向Barg？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。另外还有一个Bailout game（救助博弈），它和Barg是双向的——互相影响。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Bail和Barg的双向连接已建立。现在左侧结构还差一个Integration game？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Integr"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Integr是系统整合博弈，它同时影响Shift和Risk，起到协调作用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Integr",
        "Shift",
        "Risk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Integr到Shift和Risk的分支已完成。现在结构基本清晰了，但Press和Audit之间似乎有虚线关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Integr",
        "Shift",
        "Risk",
        "Press",
        "Audit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，Press和Audit之间是双向虚线，表示间接的反馈关联，不是直接的因果流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Press",
        "Audit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "双向虚线已添加。现在需要区分节点类型：哪些属于博弈策略类，哪些属于风险信号类？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Press",
        "Audit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Barg、Signal、Define、Shift、Place、Code、Audit、Bail、Integr这些是博弈类型，用蓝色系。Press和Risk是风险/信号类，用红色系突出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Signal",
        "Define",
        "Shift",
        "Place",
        "Code",
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Integr",
        "Press",
        "Risk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "颜色分类已应用。Press作为核心枢纽，需要更强调——加深红色填充和边框？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，Press用最深的红色，它是整个公共信号机制的核心。检查一下圆角和字体大小是否统一？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "所有节点rx/ry统一为14px，字体16px。等等，发现一个问题：Audit到Define的方向我之前画反了，应该是Audit指向Define，不是Define指向Audit。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，合规审计的结果影响定义博弈，方向别搞反。修正后整体逻辑就闭环了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "已修正Audit到Define的箭头方向。再确认一下：Barg和Bail是双向实线，Press和Audit是双向虚线，没错吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
